stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR
    [*] --> pending_registration : mint<br/>(CSPRNG,<br/>delivered via SSH)
    pending_registration --> registered : handshake verified
    registered --> registered : reconnect<br/>(same token)
    registered --> rotating : periodic (24h)<br/>or admin
    rotating --> registered : challenge response<br/>new token issued
    registered --> revoked : admin revokes
    rotating --> revoked : admin revokes
    revoked --> [*] : WebSocket closed<br/>(RevokedAuthToken)
